 yaha kahakara bhagatajii ghara kii oora jeise hii cale khuda coodharii doodxaqkara unake gale se lipatxa gae
 isase desha kaa utpaadana tathaa nivesha badxhaeqge
 ghiisuu ko usa vakata txhaakura kii baraata yaada aayii jisase biisa saala pahale vaha gayaa thaa
 aba to use acchii taraha maaluuma ho gayaa kii yaha noojavaana mana kaa pakkaa oora saahasii hei
 oora vaha donoq haatha aakaasha meq utxhaakara katxe pedxaq kii bhaamqtii bistara para gira padxii
 vaha turaqta samajha gayaa kii jaruura koii ashubha ghatxanaa ghatxita huyii hei
